company_summary:
Your Trusted Albuquerque Plumbing & HVAC Experts
In 2010 Daniels Plumbing, Heating and Air Conditioning, LLC was founded with the promise to give his customers something different. Offering a full range of plumbing, heating, cooling, and air quality services for both residential and commercial properties he set out to redefine customer satisfaction, giving people in New Mexico the specialized services they needed and the individual attention they so rightfully deserved.
Cash; Check Mastercard; Visa; American Express; Discover;

Liberty specializes in heating, cooling, and air quality. We continue to raise the bar in our industry with continued education and industry training, which allows us to adapt with technology. Lennox is the only heating and cooling system that is solar-ready. Find out how you can reduce your carbon imprint. 

Have you replaced your heating and cooling system yet? If your system is more than 15 years old, you may want to seriously consider the current rebate and tax credit promotions. The Federal Tax Credit up to $500 is a major incentive, not to mention the energy rebates. Connexus is currently offering rebates of $330 to install an air-source heat pump that meets 16 SEER. CenterPoint is offering up to $425 for a 96% efficient furnace and programmable thermostat. And, since we are a Dave Lennox Premier Dealer, we can offer rebates up to $1,400 for high-efficiency systems (exp. June 3, 2011) – which is a HUGE benefit to the homeowner. 

What does it mean to be a Dave Lennox “Premier” Dealer? It means Premier Dealers are:

1) Committed to ensuring your complete satisfaction – in terms of both the products you choose and service you receive;
2) Regularly evaluated through an independent customer-satisfaction survey process, where the customer is invited to participate and share their opinions after the completion of a job;
3) And, trained to design, install, service, and maintain home comfort and indoor air quality systems.

